  9	 *   dist/skills/{name}/references/*.md       -- Optional bundled companion guides
 10	 *   dist/standalone/{name}-skill.md          -- Frontmatter-stripped single skill markdown
 11	 *   dist/standalone/liminal-spec-skill-pack.zip
